<F_R_OG_MASH_MEASURED>1.0500000</F_R_OG_MASH_MEASURED>
<F_R_OG_MASH_MEASURED_SET>0</F_R_OG_MASH_MEASURED_SET>
<F_R_NOTES>Baked 2kg pumpkin chunks at 170C until mostly sweet and soft. 
Squashed pumpkin with potatoe masher.
After this was left with 1.3kg pumpkin pulp.
One third went in the mash, one third in at 60min, one third in at 1 min.
All the trub from the pot got pitched into primary.
Substituted Robertson &quot;Mixed Spice&quot; for Allspice.
Bottled half as is, half with an additional charge of spices (same as the 1 min addition)</F_R_NOTES>
