<F_R_NOTES>Baked 2kg pumpkin chunks @ 170 until soft and sweet. Pulped with a potato masher. Remaining mass 1.2kg.
Half the pumpkin went into the mash, half into primary via end of the boil.
Stuck mash sent efficiency to hell, corrected with DME.

Spice mix this time:
1tsp Cinnamon
1tsp Nutmeg
0.5tsp Ginger
0.5tsp Mixed Spice</F_R_NOTES>
<F_R_RATING>33.0000000</F_R_RATING>
<F_R_DESCRIPTION>Served at SY Summer Fest 2014, not judged there.
Entered into Devils Peak speciality beer competition 2014, where two of three judges suggested not using pumpkin next time.</F_R_DESCRIPTION>
