<F_G_NOTES>2kg soaked overnight
Converted for 1hr at 65C
Dried for 4+hr at 120C 
Roasted for 15min at 180C
Dried for another 1+hr at 120C

Process problems: large quantity made for a struggle drying out, resulting in extra caramelisation. Visually similar to Caraaroma, this data based on that profile.</F_G_NOTES>
