<F_R_NOTES>1067 pre boil, 1080 postboil
Split the wort into 2 fermenters (11l each)
Topped each up to 22l @ 1040.
Made 2l hop tea: 20min 3l boil, 15g Southern Passion at each of 30, 15, 0 min.
Pitched WB06 into one fermenter
Added hop tea and pitched US05 into the other fermenter</F_R_NOTES>
