<F_S_DESCRIPTION>This style is intended for combinations of existing styles (Classic Beers or Specialty-Type) that are not defined elsewhere in the guidelines. If a &lsquo;mixed-style beer&rsquo; does fit another style, do not enter it here.  Based on the declared base styles. As with all Specialty-Type Beers, the resulting combination of beer styles needs to be harmonious and balanced, and be pleasant to drink. Entry Instructions: The entrant must specify the styles being mixed. The entrant may provide an additional description of the sensory profile of the beer or the vital statistics of the resulting beer. </F_S_DESCRIPTION>
<F_S_PROFILE>OG, FG, IBUs, SRM and ABV will vary depending on the declared base styles.</F_S_PROFILE>
<F_S_INGREDIENTS>Varies with declared base styles.</F_S_INGREDIENTS>
